shared fx_lookup_instituut = let
  fx_lookup_instituut = (input as binary) =>
let
  source = input,
  importCsv = Csv.Document(Source, [Delimiter = ";", Columns = 9, Encoding = 65001, QuoteStyle = QuoteStyle.None]),
  getSemester = importCsv [Column2]{0},
  addNimikeySemester = Table.AddColumn(Table.AddColumn(Table.PromoteHeaders(Table.RemoveFirstN(importCsv, 1)), "nimikey", each Text.Select(Text.Lower([nimi]&[perenimi]), {"a".."z"}), type text), "semester", each getSemester, type text),
  addKood = 
    Table.AddColumn(addNimikeySemester, "instituudikood", each List.Accumulate(
      List.Numbers(0, Table.RowCount(_lookup_instituut)), 
      [instituut], 
      (state, current) => Text.Replace(
          state, 
          _lookup_instituut[instituut]{current}, 
          _lookup_instituut[instituudi kood]{current}
      )
    ), type text),
  selectCols = Table.SelectColumns(addKood, {"nimikey", "semester", "instituudikood"})
in
  selectCols
in
  fx_lookup_instituut;
shared fxCleanComments = let
  fxCleanComments = (input as binary) =>
let
    csvTbl = 
        Table.RenameColumns(
            Table.TransformColumns(
                Table.AddColumn(
                    Table.PromoteHeaders(
                        Csv.Document(input, [Delimiter = ";", Encoding = 65001, QuoteStyle = QuoteStyle.None]), 
                        [PromoteAllScalars=true]
                    ), 
                    "oppejoukey", 
                    each Text.Select(Text.Lower([õppejõu andmed]), {"a".."z"}), 
                    type text
                    ),
                {{"teaduskond", each Text.Start(_, 1), type text}, {"kava versiooni nimetus ", each Text.Start(_, 4)}}
                ),
        {
        {"kava versiooni nimetus ", "kava"}, 
        {"kommentaar ", "kommentaar"}, 
        {"väide", "küsimus"}, 
        {"vastus", "hinne"}
        }, 
        MissingField.Ignore),
    instituutTbl = Table.Buffer([instituut]),   
    result =  
        Table.ExpandTableColumn(
            Table.NestedJoin(
                csvTbl,
                {"oppejoukey"}, 
                instituutTbl, 
                {"nimikey"}, 
                "innerjoin", 
                JoinKind.Inner
                ),
            "innerjoin", 
            {"semester", "instituudikood"}, 
            {"semester", "instituudikood"}
        )
in result
in
  fxCleanComments;

let 
Source = input,

addKood = 
  Table.AddColumn(addNimikeySemester, "instituudikood", each List.Accumulate(
    List.Numbers(0, Table.RowCount(_lookup_instituut)), 
    [instituut], 
    (state, current) => Text.Replace(
        state, 
        _lookup_instituut[instituut]{current}, 
        _lookup_instituut[instituudi kood]{current}
    )
  ), type text),
selectCols = Table.SelectColumns(addKood, {"nimikey", "semester", "instituudikood"})

selectCols

  fxGetOppejoudsemesterkey;

shared _testKeskhindedKomentaarid = let
    Source = _folderKeskhindedKomentaarid,

            Table.NestedJoin(
                Table.RenameColumns(
                        Table.TransformColumns(
                            Table.AddColumn(
                                Table.PromoteHeaders(
                                    Csv.Document([Content], [Delimiter = ";", Encoding = 65001, QuoteStyle = QuoteStyle.None]), 
                                    [PromoteAllScalars=true]
                                ), 
                                "oppejoukey", 
                                each Text.Select(Text.Lower([õppejõu andmed]), {"a".."z"}), 
                                type text
                                ),
                            {{"teaduskond", each Text.Start(_, 1), type text}, {"kava versiooni nimetus ", each Text.Start(_, 4)}}
                            ),
                    {
                    {"kava versiooni nimetus ", "kava"}, 
                    {"kommentaar ", "kommentaar"}, 
                    {"väide", "küsimus"}, 
                    {"vastus", "hinne"}
                    }, 
                    MissingField.Ignore),
                {"oppejoukey"}, 
                instituut, 
                {"nimikey"}, 
                "innerjoin", 
                JoinKind.Inner
                ),
                "innerjoin", 
                {"semester", "instituudikood"}, 
                {"semester", "instituudikood"}
            ) 
            in result),
    tblCombine = Table.Combine(importCsv[tbl])
in
    tblCombine;

shared fakt_oppejoudKoond = let
    Source = _folderOppejoudeKoondtabel,
    addKysimus = Table.AddColumn(Source, "kysimus", each let value = Text.BetweenDelimiters([Name], "(", ")"), 
output = try Number.FromText(value) otherwise null, 
output1 = if Text.Contains([Name], "(") then output else 0 in output1, Int64.Type),
    addSemester = Table.Sort(
Table.AddColumn(addKysimus, "semester", each let value = Text.Upper(Text.Middle([Name],10,1)), aasta1 = Text.Middle([Name], 2,2), aasta2 = Text.Middle([Name], 7,2), 
        result = if value ="S" then aasta1&value else aasta2&value 
        in result, type text),
{{"semester", Order.Descending}}),
    Custom1 = Table.AddColumn(addSemester, "Custom", each 
Table.RenameColumns(Table.ReplaceValue(Table.PromoteHeaders(Table.RemoveFirstN( Csv.Document([Content], [Delimiter=";", Columns=9, Encoding =65001]),1)), ".",",",Replacer.ReplaceText,{"keskmine", "vastanute protsent(%) "}), {"vastanute protsent(%) ",  "vastanute protsent(%)"}),
type table),
    #"Removed Other Columns" = Table.SelectColumns(Custom1,{"Custom", "semester", "kysimus"}),
    #"Expanded Custom" = Table.ExpandTableColumn(#"Removed Other Columns", "Custom", {"nimi", "perenimi", "keskmine", "ainekood", "instituut", "deklareerinute arv", "vastanute arv", "vastanute protsent(%)"}, {"nimi", "perenimi", "keskmine", "ainekood", "instituut", "deklareerinute arv", "vastanute arv", "vastanute protsent(%)"}),
    #"Filtered Rows" = Table.SelectRows(#"Expanded Custom", each ([#"vastanute protsent(%)"] <> "######## ") and ([instituut] <> "Spordikeskus")),
    #"Changed Type" = Table.TransformColumnTypes(#"Filtered Rows",{{"nimi", type text}, {"perenimi", type text}, {"keskmine", type number}, {"instituut", type text}, {"deklareerinute arv", Int64.Type}, {"vastanute arv", Int64.Type}, {"vastanute protsent(%)", type number}, {"ainekood", type text}}, "de-DE"),
    #"Merged Columns" = Table.CombineColumns(#"Changed Type",{"nimi", "perenimi"},Combiner.CombineTextByDelimiter(" ", QuoteStyle.None),"nimi"),
  #"Merged queries" = Table.NestedJoin(#"Merged Columns", {"instituut"}, _lookup_instituut, {"instituut"}, "_lookup_instituut", JoinKind.LeftOuter),
  #"Expanded _lookup_instituut" = Table.ExpandTableColumn(#"Merged queries", "_lookup_instituut", {"instituudi kood"}, {"instituudikood"})
in
    #"Expanded _lookup_instituut";
shared dim_semester = let
    Source = fakt_keskhindedKomentaarid,
    selectSemester = Table.Distinct(Table.SelectColumns( Source, {"semester"})),
    addOppeaasta = Table.AddColumn(selectSemester, "oppeaasta", each Text.BeforeDelimiter([semester], " - "), type text),
    addSmster = Table.AddColumn(addOppeaasta, "smster", each if Text.Contains([semester], "kevad") then Text.Middle([semester],7,2)&"K" else if Text.Contains([semester], "sügis") then Text.Middle([semester],2,2)&"S" else "NA"),
    #"Sorted Rows" = Table.Sort(addSmster,{{"oppeaasta", Order.Ascending}})
in
